&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is all the fun parts of being a Founder without nearly as much of the pain. You will go 0-1 and scale products repeatedly. Team members who succeed in this role will likely go on to start their own companies. We would consider that a successful hire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You bring the entrepreneurial spirit. Haize brings the agent foundry, research talent, distribution, experience, compensation, and capital to enable you to sprint faster and swing bigger than you could starting from scratch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for people who are ridiculously high agency and ridiculously high urgency: individuals who start without waiting for instructions. Individuals who think on the fly and unblock themselves. Individuals who evolve with the problem, own the outcome, and deliver.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build agents for almost any business you can imagine&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Become a renaissance engineer, i.e. an expert across many domains&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unlock “apex distributors” in each vertical&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn the lingua franca of each vertical&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Originate and execute unconventional GTM strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spend a LOT of time with the customer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rapidly (&amp;lt;24 hours) prototype solutions&lt;/li&gt;
